# SauceDemo Playwright — User Workflow Automation

A modular Playwright test suite that introduces a **workflow layer** above
the Page Objects — reusable, named user actions that combine authentication,
form filling, navigation, and data entry into single callable methods.

---

## 📋 Project Overview

This project extends the multi-browser Playwright suite with a dedicated
`workflows/` package. Each workflow class represents what a real user
*does* — not just what a page *contains*. Test classes call workflow
methods like `auth.loginAsStandardUser()` and `checkout.completeFullCheckout()`
without touching a single CSS selector or page interaction directly.

A `UserData` class centralises all credentials and form values so a
Credential change is a one-file fix.

---

## 🏗️ Architecture
src/test/java/
├── base/
│   └── BaseTest.java              # Playwright lifecycle + ThreadLocal<Page>
├── data/
│   └── UserData.java              # All credentials and form values
├── pages/
│   ├── LoginPage.java
│   ├── InventoryPage.java
│   ├── CartPage.java
│   ├── CheckoutInfoPage.java
│   ├── CheckoutOverviewPage.java
│   └── ConfirmationPage.java
├── workflows/
│   ├── AuthWorkflow.java          # Login, logout, locked-out scenarios
│   ├── NavigationWorkflow.java    # URL navigation and page title reading
│   ├── ShoppingWorkflow.java      # Add to cart, badge count, multi-item
│   └── CheckoutWorkflow.java      # Cart → form → overview → confirmation
└── tests/
├── AuthWorkflowTest.java      # 4 auth scenarios
├── ShoppingWorkflowTest.java  # 4 shopping scenarios
└── CheckoutWorkflowTest.java  # 4 checkout step assertions

---

## ✅ Test Scenarios

### `AuthWorkflowTest`
| # | Test | What it validates |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | `testValidLogin` | Standard user reaches the inventory page |
| 2 | `testInvalidPassword` | Wrong password shows credential mismatch error |
| 3 | `testLockedOutUser` | Locked account shows locked-out error |
| 4 | `testLogout` | Logout returns to the login page URL |

### `ShoppingWorkflowTest`
| # | Test | What it validates |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | `testInventoryLoads` | Product grid visible and title reads "Products" |
| 2 | `testAddSingleItemToCart` | Cart badge updates to "1" |
| 3 | `testAddMultipleItemsToCart` | Cart badge updates to "3" |
| 4 | `testNavigateToCart` | Cart icon opens the cart page |

### `CheckoutWorkflowTest`
| # | Test | What it validates |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | `testOpenCart` | Cart page loads with correct title |
| 2 | `testProceedToCheckout` | Checkout form page loads |
| 3 | `testFillCheckoutInformation` | Form submission reaches order overview |
| 4 | `testFinishOrder` | Confirmation message is displayed |

