| **Maven** | — | Dependency management and build |

---

## 💡 Concepts Demonstrated

- **Workflow layer** — business-level actions sit above page objects,
  keeping test methods intention-revealing and selector-free
- **Data centralisation** — `UserData` owns all credentials and form
  values; tests never contain hardcoded strings
- **Negative testing** — invalid password and locked-out user scenarios
  exercise error paths, not just the happy path
- **`waitForFunction()`** — JavaScript polling waits for precise badge
  count values rather than fixed timeouts
- **`@BeforeClass` login** — authentication runs once per class,
  not before every individual test method

---

## 🚀 How to Run

mvn exec:java -e -D exec.mainClass=com.microsoft.playwright.CLI -D exec.args="install"

mvn test
mvn test -Dsuite=testng-chromium
mvn test -Dsuite=testng-firefox
mvn test -Dsuite=testng-webkit
```
